description:
Stewart is a 21-year-old bartender from the east coast.
"I love it," he said, referring to his job. "I get to meet all kinds of people."
"Don't you have to deal with them getting messy sometimes?" I asked.
"Oh sure," he replied. "But that's half the fun!"
Stewart has lived in the same place all his life, but he travels a lot.
"My girl friend is a flight attendant," he told us. "She gets free tickets, so we go together a lot."
Stewart also loves sports.
"I was big into lacrosse in high school. I also played football and I wrestled."
title: Stewart
